        public java.util.Set<Tuple<Node<T>,Node<T>>> createProgram(int time,
                                                  DeferredSchedulingNode<T> node,
                                                  network.VOQScheduler.Tag tag)
        Description copied from class: VOQScheduler
        Generates a plan for message transmission at the supplied node and time. This method should not transmit any messages, as this is taken care of in VOQScheduler.scheduleNode(int, DeferredSchedulingNode).
        Specified by:
        createProgram in class VOQScheduler<T extends Message>
        Parameters:
        time - The time to create the plan at.
        node - The node to create the plan for.
        tag - The tag of the node.
        Returns:
        Returns the set of edges to schedule at the supplied time and for the supplied node.
